Pengurus awak dan saya perlu berbincang.

00:42:21.850 --> 00:42:22.710
Okay. jom pergi.

00:42:37.070 --> 00:42:37.290
"Ping"?

00:42:37.290 --> 00:42:38.590
[Ping]

00:42:38.590 --> 00:42:39.140
ya.

00:42:39.230 --> 00:42:40.230
siapa nama awak?

00:42:40.230 --> 00:42:40.890
Gu Pingwen.

00:42:40.920 --> 00:42:41.440
betul tu.

